      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>When most people think about hypnosis they get scared and imagine themselves running around a stage like a headless chicken. But if you really want to learn the <strong>secret of self hypnosis</strong> you need to put aside all your doubts and keep reading every word of this article.</p>
<div style="padding: 5px; float: right;"><a title="Secret of Self Hypnosis" href="http://www.ehypnosisinduction.com/course" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4018/4408931003_170bd3a20c_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Secret of Self Hypnosis Images" width="240" height="180" title="Secret of Self Hypnosis   3 Simple Step to a Better Life Now!" /></a><br />
<small>credit: <a title="AlishaV" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/31169339@N07/4408931003/" target="_blank">AlishaV</a></small></div>
<p>You see, real hypnosis in not about mind control and brain washing, the real secret is that you can give your subconscious mind commands that it will obey and make positive changes in your life. The reason this works so well is because the subconscious does not have a critical faculty which means that it will believe any message that it hears enough.</p>
<p>There are many ways you can use hypnosis for positive change in your life and one of the first is self hypnosis.</p>
<p>This is great because you don’t have to spend a lot of money on a professional hypnotists and you can start to see some of the benefits right away.</p>
<h2><strong>The Secret of Self Hypnosis Revealed</strong></h2>
<p>1. The reason people like self hypnosis is because you don’t have to give over control to an outside hypnotist. All you have to do is work out what you want to achieve and how long you want to be under each day.</p>
<p>2. There are a lot of ways that you can perform self hypnosis but I think the very best is to get a CD. This works so well because you don’t have to have any skills. You just buy the CD and then listen to it everyday for an hour of so.</p>
<p>3. The way the CD works is that each one will focus on some aspect of your life that you would like to enhance. Like giving up smoking for instance. Once you have been guided into trace you will then be given positive messages direct into your subconscious that will make smoking seem stupid.</p>
<p>4. The <em>secret of self hypnosis</em> is that it can help with all manner of problems in you life and even disease. The reason for this is that if you are ill and are constantly feeling down your immune system will be low and you will get worse. But if you use positive self hypnosis you will start to feel like there is nothing wrong with you and pretty soon you will be fine.</p>
