<p>In this article we’re going to look at how you might learn to <strong>hypnotize someone without them knowing</strong>, and it all comes down to one simple tactic that you can learn without too much trouble&#8230;</p>
<div style="padding: 5px; float: right;"><a title="Hypnotize Someone Without Them Knowing" href="http://www.ehypnosisinduction.com/course" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4001/4311053346_f01c8df773_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Hypnotize Someone Without Them Knowing" width="160" height="240" title="Hypnotize Someone Without Them Knowing   100% FREE Tips, Here!" /></a><br />
<small>credit: <a title="quinn.anya" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/53326337@N00/4311053346/" target="_blank">quinn.anya</a></small></div>
<p>Covert hypnosis!</p>
<p>This is the process of putting the subject into trance with just hypnotics words. You don’t even have to get them to shut their eyes and it&#8217;s not too difficult to learn.</p>
<p>Now let’s look at a few of the things you can do to get this working for you.</p>
<h2>4 Steps to Hypnotize Someone Without Them Knowing</h2>
<p>1. Think about you voice &#8211; this is the most important part of learning <em>hypnotize someone without them knowing</em>, because you need to combine you tone, pitch and the actual words to make it effective. Have a look at some hypnosis videos on YouTube and think about how they talk.</p>
<p>2. Body language &#8211; this is also very important and to build rapport you need to think about how you act around close friends and family.</p>
<p>3. Be an observer &#8211; you need to start noticing subtle changes in your subject. One common part of covert hypnosis is to mirror the breathing which will build rapport even faster.</p>
<p>4. Be a master &#8211; this simply means that you should learn everything you can about covert hypnosis before you ever start to practice on people. This because you will often be in a situation where you have induced a trance and will not know where to go from there.</p>
<p>Final thoughts.</p>
<p>You will not learn this skill over night but if you practice everyday you will easily be able to hypnotize someone without them knowing.</p>
<p>The only other thing I would say is that this kind of hypnosis works best when you use it in a positive way. You’re not trying to be evil here, you just want to stack the odds in your favor  and use just a little convert hypnosis every day to make things go your way.</p>
<p>If you just follow that simple rule your life will be on an upward spiral.</p>
