      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>The simple answer to “<strong>does self hypnosis work</strong>?” is Yes. For confidence, smoking, panic, depress, pain relief and many more you can always use the power of the subconscious mind to make things flow much more smoothly in your life.</p>
<div style="padding: 5px; float: right;"><a title="Does Self Hypnosis Work" href="http://www.ehypnosisinduction.com/course" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2275/3595827169_952f0fed88_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Does Self Hypnosis Work Images" width="157" height="240" title="Does Self Hypnosis Work   Advice for Confused People, Read Here!" /></a><br />
<small>credit: <a title="abbasj812" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/38375554@N05/3595827169/" target="_blank">abbasj812</a></small></div>
<p>The use of self hypnosis comes in many forms but the easiest way to get started is with a recording. Because you don’t have to make any effort, you just listen to the audio every day and then positive chances start to occur in your life.</p>
<p>So all you have to do is decide what you want to achieve then jump onto google and get the super cheap recordings&#8230;simple.</p>
<p>The reason that subliminal self hypnosis works so well is that your subconscious mind does not decide what to believe. If it hears “I’m a millionaire” enough times it will believe it and you will start to notice money making ideas all over the place.</p>
<blockquote>
<h2>Does Self Hypnosis Work &#8211; Yes!</h2>
</blockquote>
<p>The is the real power of the “secret” not some amazing gift given to you by the universe. It’s your power to notice opportunities that is being enhanced.</p>
<p>Below you will find some tips to make self hypnosis work for you.</p>
<p>1. Before you listen to the recording you must make sure that you are not going to be disrupted half way though. Let your family know that you are going to be away for half an hour and then find a quiet room and look the door. This may sound harsh but it is super important.</p>
<p>2. Clear your mind of thoughts about your day. You can do this by just noticing your breathing.</p>
<p>3. Become relaxed. Most of the time the recording will help you with this.</p>
<p>4. Make sure that you choose the change that is going to have the most positive effect in your life. For instance if you smoke but also want to make a million dollars I would go for the smoking first because it will help with all other aspects of your life.</p>
<p>5. You need to make self hypnosis a daily habit because changes never happen over night. It might take your a year to achieve your goal but as long as you have the unbreakable daily habit you will get there in the end.</p>
<p>I hope that helped you find out <em>Does Self Hypnosis Work</em>?</p>
