      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Cover hypnosis is the holy grail for a lot of people because using the <strong>covert hypnosis manual operator</strong> means you can take control of another persons mind and bend their actions to suite your will.</p>
<div style="padding: 5px; float: right;"><a title="Covert Hypnosis Manual Operator" href="http://www.ehypnosisinduction.com/course" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4147/5107760838_a45ce4dde2_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Covert Hypnosis Manual Operator Images" width="176" height="240" title="Covert Hypnosis Manual Operator: Hypnotize Anyone, Any Time!" /></a><br />
<small>credit: <a title="jimcrotty.com" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/86016750@N00/5107760838/" target="_blank">jimcrotty.com</a></small></div>
<p>In this article you are going to lean the <em>covert hypnosis manual operator</em> that will allow you to gain a deep knowledge of suggestion. This will allow you to command others to do what you ask, without them even knowing that any hypnosis is happening at all.</p>
<p>STEP 1 &#8211; You need to get attention and gain rapport</p>
<p>Without the full attention of your subject you will never be able to induce hypnosis, and building a good rapport will let you put them in a relaxed state with words that seem magnetic.</p>
<p>1. You should listen very closely to your subject and even lean in a little.<br />
2. You should smile when they are talking and show that you are very enthusiastic about what they are saying.<br />
3. Show that you have the same interests and past times.<br />
4. The last part is to test if you have rapport with the body language check. You can do this by crossing you arms or legs and seeing if they copy you.</p>
<p>STEP 2 &#8211; Time for the trance.</p>
<p>In covert hypnosis the trance is the most tricky part. You are not going to be able to take them though the usual script or swing a pendulum back and forth in front of their eyes. So you need to be more subtle and have the person hanging off your every word.</p>
<p>To master this most difficult task you should study people in power and ask yourself what it is about them that makes you believe even word they say instantly. Powerful people are often those who have studied the covert hypnosis manual operator.</p>
<p>STEP 3 &#8211; Make some initial suggestions</p>
<p>At some point you are going to have to take the bull by the horns and actually start to offer suggestions, to see if your trance is working and if you have enough rapport. The best way to do this is by using sentences that already suggest that you are right and that they should be listening to what you say.</p>
<h2>Top 3 Covert Hypnosis Manual Operator</h2>
<p>There are 3 examples below and you can start to make up you own once you have the idea:</p>
<p>* I’m going to the mall today, come with me.<br />
* We will continue this phone call tomorrow when we have the sales figures in front of us.<br />
* The fist thing you will notice about this house is the light and airy rooms , the second is the the low cost compared with other homes in the area.</p>
