      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p><strong>The art of covert hypnosis</strong> is also known as conversational hypnosis to some people. For those of you that don’t know it’s basically the process of taking control of someone by talking directly to their subconscious mind without them knowing.</p>
<div style="padding: 5px; float: right;"><a title="The Art of Covert Hypnosis" href="http://www.ehypnosisinduction.com/course" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/49/144847874_fed4609508_m.jpg" border="0" alt="The Art of Covert Hypnosis" width="240" height="162" title="The Art of Covert Hypnosis: Learn BANNED Hypnosis Techniques?" /></a><br />
<small>credit: <a title="magnetbox" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/35034345533@N01/144847874/" target="_blank">magnetbox</a></small></div>
<p>This is often used by public speakers and politicians but a more sinister side is that men also sometimes use this tactic to pick up women.</p>
<p>But the thing to remember is that you can only ever use covert hypnosis to encourage someone to do something that they would have done anyway. Which is where the art of persuasion comes in.</p>
<p>You ultimate goal as a covert hypnotists is to change the opinions of the subject rather than control their mind. This method is often use to help with addictions and other debilitating disease.</p>
<blockquote>
<h2>The Art of Covert Hypnosis is not Evil!</h2>
</blockquote>
<p>But you can forget about trying to get that subject to go into trance in the conventional way by swinging a watch in front of their eyes.</p>
<p>Your goal is to just say convincing words that put them right under.</p>
<p>The first step in <em>the art of covert hypnosis</em> is always building rapport and you know how to do this already. Think about your friends and family. If you told them something they would believe it right away or even obey your commands. You need to practice meeting people for the first time and having an instant connection with them by giving truthful compliment and being interested.</p>
<p>Once you have rapport with the person you could move into telling them a hypnotic story that would put them into a trance.</p>
<p>The best way to start a hypnotic story is to use a phrase like “imagine if&#8230;”</p>
<p>This will help the subject let go of reality and give you the ability to create a new reality for them.</p>
<p>Final thoughts.</p>
<p>If you want to learn covert hypnosis just listen to politicians speak or go to your local car dealership and talk to the best salesman, they all know the secrets and you can easily learn this stuff as well.</p>
<p>I can&#8217;t tell you how much this can just make your personal relationships much deeper and more engaging.</p>
